Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Yakima Canutt, 1986
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xq9n
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 1 Jun 1986
In praise of the little-known name behind the thrilling stunts of many big-name movie stars. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less